description: This file appears to be the main application component for a React-based frontend of a movie exploration app called MovieAI. It imports multiple components such as Header, Footer, SectionCard, AddMovieForm, and MoviesList, and renders a structured layout that includes a hero section, featured and trending placeholders, and a user-specific 'My Movies' section powered by Supabase.

methods.name: App()
methods.description: Main React functional component rendering the entire application layout, including header, main content sections, and footer.
